              <div class="question" id="safe-to-use-credit-card-online">
                <b>Q: Is it safe to use my debit card online? </b> <br/>
                <b> A: </b> Yes. And please note: If you choose to pay by debit card, the amount you charge will be put
                on "hold", meaning it will not be available to you once your shipment is planned. Once your order is
                shipped, the amount of the transaction will be withdrawn from your account and the original "hold" will
                be voided.
              </div>

