              <div class="question" id="authorize-to-sale-brand">
                <b>Q: Are you authorized to sell the brands you advertise on your site? </b> <br/>
                <b> A: </b> Yes, BrandCruz.com is an authorized online retailer of all brands sold on our site, and we
